Why Choose Regular Stay Insurance?

Perfect for occasional travelers who want essential protection

Globelink Regular Stay Travel Insurance provides essential medical and repatriation cover at an affordable price. Designed for travelers who want reliable protection without unnecessary extras, this policy offers comprehensive coverage for trips up to 60 days.

Available to EU and EEA residents up to age 84, this insurance includes emergency medical expenses up to €5,000,000, personal baggage protection, and over 100 adventure activities covered as standard.

💡

  • Travelers aged up to 84
  • EU & EEA residents
